column5: I am a Senager,  I have everything I ever wanted as a teenager, only 50 years later. I don't have to go to school or work. I get an allowance ( pension). I have my own pad. I don't have a curfew. I have a drivers licence and my own car. I have ID that gets me into bars and the beer store. The girls I hang out with are not scared of getting pregnant. I don't have acne. Life is great.
Lol I was expecting to read in the last line something about not being able to remember anything haha
